overview:
ITXpertPanel is the ideal medium for bringing experienced IT professionals together virtually.

ITXpertPanel is a platform for augmenting and enhancing the knowledge and skill sets of experienced IT professionals across the globe.It is aimed at seasoned IT professionals with a high degree of qualification and experience. It seeks to address minute and intricate areas of their expertise that could have developed into their domain and seeks to clear these doubts and pain areas.
